### Session status
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/me

### Start Google login
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/google

### Connect Gmail after login
GET http://localhost:4000/api/gmail/connect

### Unified inbox search
GET http://localhost:4000/api/messages?q=campaign&provider=gmail

### Gmail sync
POST http://localhost:4000/api/gmail/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maxResults": 15
}

### Gmail message detail
GET http://localhost:4000/api/gmail/message/msg_123

### AI summary
POST http://localhost:4000/api/ai/summary
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "replace-with-message-id"
}

### AI reply suggestions
POST http://localhost:4000/api/ai/reply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageId": "replace-with-message-id",
  "tone": "professional"
}
